@NODE 301
@TITLE "Controls/Main window..."

    Main window can be controlled via:
    ŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻ
      a)  @{"  Main menu               "  LINK 302}

      b)  @{"  Icons                   "  LINK 302}

      c)  @{"  Keyboard                "  LINK 302}


    Icons (from left)
    ŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻ
    1.  New tape
    2.  Load tape
    3.  Save tape
    4.  Print tape
    5.  Preview
    6.  Swapping window
    7.  Sleep
    8.  Help


    Keyboard shortcuts
    ŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻ
      F1            - big title
      F2            - titles
      F3            - side A
      F4            - side B
      F5            - Swapping window
      F6            - print
      F7            - setup colors
      F8            - setup fonts
      F9            - setup public screen
      F10           - setup miscellaneous
      SPACE         - preview on/off
      `             - about program
      HELP          - help for main window
      SHIFT + HELP  - help content

@ENDNODE


