  Main menu have three sub-menus:
  ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

    @{"  File          " LINK 316}  load, save, print...

    @{"  Data          " LINK 317}  input data and fonts...

    @{"  Configuration " LINK 318}  setup GUI and functions...

 
@ENDNODE


@NODE 303
@TITLE "Controls/Big Title..."

  Here you can input text for big title.
  You can scale width from 25 to 175%.
  You can check center or left-aligned text.

@ENDNODE


@NODE 304
@TITLE "Controls/Side titles..."

  Here you can input texts for side titles.
  You can scale width from 25 to 175%.
  You can check automatic side names (A: and B:).

@ENDNODE


@NODE 305
@TITLE "Controls/Input songs..."

  Here you can input text for songs.
  You can scale width from 25 to 175%.
  You can use local menu functions.

  · Remarks
    ŻŻŻŻŻŻŻ
    - @ as first character will be replaced by song number
    - text may be only 80 characters long

  · Keyboard shortcuts
    ŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻ
      right AMIGA + Q       - undo
      right AMIGA + X       - clear line
      SHIFT + DEL           - clear to end
      SHIFT + BACKSPACE     - clear to begin
      SHIFT + horiz.arrows  - begin/end of line
      SHIFT + vert.arrows   - move between lines!
      TAB, SHIFT+TAB        - move between lines
      RETURN, ESC           - escape from input line
      right AMIGA + ??      - see keys in local menu!

@ENDNODE


