@NODE 400
@TITLE "Tips & tricks..."

  · List of ToolTypes
    ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
      ------------- configuration -----------------
      OPTIONS    = n        (bits)
      FLAGS      = n        (bits)
      WINXY      = x,y      (main window position)
      FILERQ     = x,y,w,h  (file requester position)
      FONTRQ     = x,y,w,h  (font requester position)
      DENSITY    = n        (print density n=1..7)
      CENTER     = ON/OFF
      PAGEFEED   = ON/OFF
      ASPECT     = n        (n=0..1)
      IMAGE      = n        (n=0..1)
      INCTITLE   = ON/OFF
      COLORMX    = n        (sel.color  n=0..6)
      COLORSET   = n        (sel.preset n=0..2)
      COLORS     = n1..n7   (custom pens)
      WIDTHS     = w1..w4   (initial widths)
      MENUFONT   = fontname / fontsize
      DIALOGFONT =       -""-
      STRINGFONT =       -""-
      TITLEFONT  =       -""-
      TEXTFONT   =       -""-
      PUBSCREEN  = public screen name
      MSGTYPE    = n  (type of messages - n=0..2)
      REQTYPE    = n  (type of requesters - n=0..2)
      ------------- special -----------------------
      DRAWER     = drawername for cassette files
      TAPEICON   = icon for cassette files  (no .info!)
      APPICON    = icon for sleep           (no .info!)
      APPXY      = x,y  (sleep icon position, -1 = no position)
      PRINTERDEV = printer driver name
      LEFT       = n1,n2  (left edge of text - in mm*10)
      TABS       = n1,n2  (min. and max. tabelators- in mm*10)
      CORRECTXDPI= n  (change width aspect from 50% to 200%)

@ENDNODE



@NODE 500
@TITLE "History..."

  · Developed on A1200/68030/50MHz/18MB with DiceC 2.0
  · Tested on A1200, A1200/030, A600, A500+, OS 2.04 thru 3.1
  · Tested with Enforcer and Mungwall


  Version 1.0 (24-Oct-1995,  69464 bytes) 
  ŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻ
    - first release

  Version 1.1 (30-Jan-1996,  77276 bytes)
  ŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻ
    - added clipboard support
    - added reqtools.library support
    - windows now have better look
    - added stack checking (8KB minimum)
    - bugfix: disabled gadgets could be selected via hotkeys
    - AppWindow/AppIcon now doesn't reflect non-existing files
    - now zoom-gadget is disabled in critical situations
    - improved main loop: zero CPU usage!
    - now you can drop icon into all windows - great!
    - now you can stop program by sending a 'break' signal
    - added support for SLIM tapes
    - added clipping when text doesn't fit into raster
    - now you can set wait time for printer (default 6 sec.)
    - now you can change relative window width from 75% to 200%
    - added auto-replacing of missing fonts
    - corrected problem with start from CLI

  Version 1.2 (22-Apr-1996,  90304 bytes)
  ŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻ
     - all read enforcer hits has been eliminated
     - improved public screen selector
     - improved program stability
     - now you can add additional information to titles (year etc.)
     - fixed bug in backfill-hook
     - added MagicWB pattern for window background
     - other small enhancements

  See @{"future releases" LINK 600}.

@ENDNODE


@NODE 600
@TITLE "Future..."

   Some ideas:
   ŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻ
     - long tapes  (30 songs!)
     - faster generation of outline fonts
     - direct call bullet.library
     - own process for print, abort
     - better WYSIWYG
     - tape tags (DATE, TIME, SOURCE, DOLBY, CHROME)
     - special, full async version 68020+/OS 3.x/MUI 3
     - simple AREXX interface
     - sound effects, speech
     - UNDO

@ENDNODE




